1
00:00:58,016 --> 00:01:00,992
=Within The Grip=

2
00:01:00,992 --> 00:01:02,962
=Episode 24=

3
00:01:03,738 --> 00:01:06,682
(Side by Side)

4
00:01:07,002 --> 00:01:09,722
(Virtue of Heaven and Earth)

5
00:01:09,888 --> 00:01:11,360
(Pavilion Master's Token)

6
00:01:11,840 --> 00:01:15,280
The Xuanji Pavilion's death guards
only obey the token without question.

7
00:01:15,799 --> 00:01:20,000
If one day, the token falls
into the wrong hands,

8
00:01:20,959 --> 00:01:22,000
are we supposed

9
00:01:22,000 --> 00:01:25,159
to become the blade in their hands
that slaughters the loyal and righteous?

10
00:01:26,640 --> 00:01:29,359
But now, it is in your hands.

11
00:01:32,400 --> 00:01:33,840
Starting today,

12
00:01:34,319 --> 00:01:38,439
you are the Master
of the Xuanji Pavilion.

13
00:01:39,719 --> 00:01:41,480
- Master
- Master.

14
00:01:41,599 --> 00:01:43,319
- Master
- Master.

15
00:01:43,480 --> 00:01:45,000
- Master
- Master.

16
00:01:50,239 --> 00:01:53,640
I'm just like any of you,
raised in the Pavilion.

17
00:01:54,439 --> 00:01:55,840
I don't know who I am,

18
00:01:56,599 --> 00:01:59,599
the purpose behind each task,

19
00:02:00,359 --> 00:02:02,439
or where tomorrow will take me.

20
00:02:03,120 --> 00:02:06,079
We're just cogs spinning
along a set track

21
00:02:07,280 --> 00:02:09,479
and blades in anyone's grasp.

22
00:02:10,280 --> 00:02:11,960
I've asked myself countless times.

23
00:02:12,919 --> 00:02:14,240
What do I truly seek?

24
00:02:14,680 --> 00:02:17,159
Freedom? Power?

25
00:02:18,599 --> 00:02:21,159
No, neither.

26
00:02:44,719 --> 00:02:49,000
I want to understand what path I walk,

27
00:02:49,639 --> 00:02:51,479
find my own way,

28
00:02:52,639 --> 00:02:55,639
make my own choices and live for myself.

29
00:02:57,719 --> 00:03:00,960
Even if this path must be walked alone,

30
00:03:02,199 --> 00:03:06,000
I hope each of you finds your own way.

31
00:03:29,439 --> 00:03:30,360
You're not dead?

32
00:03:32,240 --> 00:03:35,240
Did you expect me to die
in the bamboo grove outside the city

33
00:03:35,599 --> 00:03:38,039
or at the wedding days ago?

34
00:03:39,840 --> 00:03:41,000
So it was you.

35
00:03:42,360 --> 00:03:45,759
After all these years of your care,

36
00:03:46,240 --> 00:03:47,599
how should I repay it?

37
00:03:48,080 --> 00:03:53,280
Pity that blades don't know mercy.
Don't resist pointlessly.

38
00:03:54,120 --> 00:03:56,159
You deceived me with two fake deaths!

39
00:03:59,039 --> 00:04:00,439
Do you really believe

40
00:04:00,439 --> 00:04:03,560
disguises and voice changes
could fool the Xuanji Pavilion?

41
00:04:04,800 --> 00:04:06,159
For your plan,

42
00:04:07,400 --> 00:04:08,960
you even disfigured that person.

43
00:04:10,120 --> 00:04:13,159
Or did you think after Chief He's death,

44
00:04:13,159 --> 00:04:15,439
no one would suspect you?

45
00:04:16,959 --> 00:04:20,439
Chief He served Father
for years with utmost caution.

46
00:04:20,959 --> 00:04:23,519
No one ever uncovered
his close ties to your mother

47
00:04:23,879 --> 00:04:25,240
or to the Right Chancellor...

48
00:04:26,879 --> 00:04:29,480
no, your grandfather.

49
00:04:30,920 --> 00:04:35,519
He even destroyed the secret tunnels
for the messenger hamster.

50
00:04:36,600 --> 00:04:39,639
Pity even the tightest plan has flaws.

51
00:04:39,879 --> 00:04:42,319
The Heaven task was issued
before the hamster returned.

52
00:04:42,360 --> 00:04:43,720
It narrowly avoided disaster.

53
00:04:57,920 --> 00:04:59,319
It's just a mouse.

54
00:05:03,439 --> 00:05:05,800
The Pavilion's Heaven tasks
are highly secret.

55
00:05:06,360 --> 00:05:08,759
But they can't appear
by magic in the Shadow Pavilion.

56
00:05:09,319 --> 00:05:09,959
You can

57
00:05:10,439 --> 00:05:12,920
start investigating
from the capital's drainage pipes.

58
00:05:21,399 --> 00:05:26,120
The hamster led us through the tunnels
to the Right Chancellor's mansion.

59
00:05:26,720 --> 00:05:29,319
Whether it was Gu Wenshuang, Chief He,

60
00:05:29,839 --> 00:05:32,680
or the Right Chancellor,
they all shielded you well.

61
00:05:33,560 --> 00:05:37,040
With no evidence against you,
I could only step back

62
00:05:38,480 --> 00:05:39,639
in order to pull you in.

63
00:05:54,920 --> 00:05:56,560
The ultimate winner is still me.

64
00:05:57,680 --> 00:06:01,399
Useless. My agents lurk near him.

65
00:06:01,600 --> 00:06:02,680
Fireworks signal the order.

66
00:06:03,360 --> 00:06:08,399
If you value his life, release me now.

67
00:06:13,199 --> 00:06:14,800
My dear brother.

68
00:06:15,120 --> 00:06:17,439
Why do you care
so deeply about his life?

69
00:06:18,120 --> 00:06:20,360
You should hate him as I do.

70
00:06:20,560 --> 00:06:23,160
Your mother's death
condemned you to years of suffering.

71
00:06:24,079 --> 00:06:27,920
You were sidelined for so long
because of his incompetence.

72
00:06:29,560 --> 00:06:31,399
If I die with him today,

73
00:06:31,800 --> 00:06:33,360
even if you inherit the throne,

74
00:06:34,160 --> 00:06:37,279
how will you silence public criticism?

75
00:06:40,480 --> 00:06:43,839
You're right.
I care nothing for his life.

76
00:06:44,839 --> 00:06:46,920
Today, I can spare your life.

77
00:06:47,800 --> 00:06:51,600
Father failed to discipline you,
but I cannot take his place.

78
00:06:52,519 --> 00:06:57,040
So I'm sending you to the royal tombs
to keep your mother company.

79
00:06:57,959 --> 00:06:58,879
You dare?

80
00:07:00,839 --> 00:07:01,720
Why wouldn't I dare?

81
00:07:02,120 --> 00:07:02,879
Take him away.

82
00:07:06,160 --> 00:07:07,240
I haven't lost yet.

83
00:07:09,279 --> 00:07:10,279
I haven't lost.

84
00:07:10,360 --> 00:07:12,360
Your Highness, regarding His Majesty...

85
00:07:15,920 --> 00:07:18,000
Some words, some things,

86
00:07:19,240 --> 00:07:22,160
once missed, bring endless regret.

87
00:07:23,360 --> 00:07:26,120
In life, what is true or false?

88
00:07:26,439 --> 00:07:30,040
Don't wait until regret consumes you.

89
00:07:54,759 --> 00:07:55,800
Your Majesty, watch out!

90
00:07:55,800 --> 00:07:56,879
Guards! Protect me!

91
00:07:58,600 --> 00:07:59,720
Someone help!

92
00:07:59,720 --> 00:08:00,879
Assassin!

93
00:08:02,120 --> 00:08:05,120
Help! Someone!

94
00:08:10,720 --> 00:08:12,240
Protect His Majesty!

95
00:08:12,879 --> 00:08:13,399
Guards!

96
00:08:13,399 --> 00:08:14,319
Seize them!

97
00:08:32,320 --> 00:08:32,919
Be careful!

98
00:08:50,200 --> 00:08:51,120
Watch out!

99
00:09:55,399 --> 00:09:57,080
Don't waste your effort.

100
00:09:57,480 --> 00:09:59,159
I know

101
00:10:01,879 --> 00:10:03,279
my own body.

102
00:10:10,840 --> 00:10:14,919
Before, the residual poison
in my body wasn't cleared.

103
00:10:15,559 --> 00:10:19,440
Now, I've been poisoned
by a hidden weapon, and I'm done for.

104
00:10:20,759 --> 00:10:23,960
You look so much like your mother.

105
00:10:26,320 --> 00:10:29,679
Your mother, Yun Sui,

106
00:10:30,200 --> 00:10:32,720
was the best woman in the world.

107
00:10:32,759 --> 00:10:35,320
She single-handedly
founded the Xuanji Pavilion.

108
00:10:35,360 --> 00:10:36,799
- Master.
- Master.

109
00:10:37,240 --> 00:10:42,279
(From that moment on,
I was smitten with her.)

110
00:10:46,200 --> 00:10:49,399
It's just a pity that she fell
in love with Qin Yuheng.

111
00:10:50,480 --> 00:10:54,039
But Qin Yuheng married someone else
for the sake of his family.

112
00:10:54,559 --> 00:10:56,960
After Yun Sui severed ties with him,

113
00:10:57,879 --> 00:10:59,240
she discovered

114
00:11:01,039 --> 00:11:02,759
that she was already pregnant with you.

115
00:11:03,320 --> 00:11:05,039
She was heartbroken.

116
00:11:05,159 --> 00:11:08,200
I wanted to make her my wife.

117
00:11:09,720 --> 00:11:12,799
I never expected that our marriage

118
00:11:13,200 --> 00:11:16,159
would cause Qin Yuheng
to be consumed by inner demons.

119
00:11:16,720 --> 00:11:18,399
He became deranged

120
00:11:19,120 --> 00:11:21,600
and slaughtered his entire family.

121
00:11:21,600 --> 00:11:22,938
(Left Chancellor's Mansion)

122
00:11:23,799 --> 00:11:25,879
(When I arrived at his mansion,)

123
00:11:26,639 --> 00:11:31,399
(the place was a river of blood,
and only he remained.)

124
00:11:36,840 --> 00:11:38,200
It was me.

125
00:11:40,360 --> 00:11:41,759
I killed him.

126
00:11:43,600 --> 00:11:47,960
I indeed killed your father.

127
00:11:49,639 --> 00:11:53,240
Later, Lianyi had an accident
after entering the palace.

128
00:11:54,879 --> 00:11:56,639
I couldn't save her.

129
00:11:57,879 --> 00:12:02,399
(I only managed to snatch back
the child taken by the assassins.)

130
00:12:02,960 --> 00:12:07,120
(That child was Gu Zhaoxi.)

131
00:12:10,799 --> 00:12:14,279
At that time, Yun Sui
had just given birth to you.

132
00:12:15,840 --> 00:12:17,720
We knew there was trouble in the palace.

133
00:12:18,360 --> 00:12:20,600
To protect Lianyi's child,

134
00:12:21,600 --> 00:12:24,399
she reluctantly left you
at the Xuanji Pavilion.

135
00:12:24,879 --> 00:12:26,559
Then she took Lianyi's child

136
00:12:27,799 --> 00:12:29,879
under the guise of her own child

137
00:12:30,679 --> 00:12:32,399
and brought him back to our family.

138
00:12:35,240 --> 00:12:39,360
We thought about
investigating in secret.

139
00:12:39,960 --> 00:12:43,720
But the Pavilion's secrecy rules

140
00:12:44,759 --> 00:12:49,039
and the palace's blockade of information

141
00:12:49,559 --> 00:12:51,519
caused Yun Sui, who went to investigate,

142
00:12:52,879 --> 00:12:54,080
to finally...

143
00:12:59,840 --> 00:13:01,960
It's my fault for what happened to her.

144
00:13:19,802 --> 00:13:22,650
(Hanzhang Hall)

145
00:13:23,799 --> 00:13:25,039
Let what happened yesterday

146
00:13:26,159 --> 00:13:28,600
be an end to all these years.

147
00:13:30,039 --> 00:13:31,919
The Xuanji Pavilion
has protected me well.

148
00:13:32,480 --> 00:13:34,759
I posthumously name Gu Jiang
as Marquis of Yong'an.

149
00:13:35,000 --> 00:13:38,320
The eldest son of the Gu family
may inherit the title for generations.

150
00:13:42,480 --> 00:13:43,519
Thank you, Your Majesty.

151
00:13:46,039 --> 00:13:50,159
I never expected Yin Huan
to have been scheming for so many years.

152
00:13:50,720 --> 00:13:53,559
Since he's cast aside our kinship,

153
00:13:54,279 --> 00:13:56,360
I shall act as if I never had this son.

154
00:13:58,159 --> 00:14:01,440
Hand him and the Right Chancellor over
to the Law Tribunal for punishment.

155
00:14:01,919 --> 00:14:03,279
Yes, Your Majesty.

156
00:14:06,519 --> 00:14:09,919
Zhou, is there any reward you want?

157
00:14:13,882 --> 00:14:18,799
(Hanzhang Hall)

158
00:14:18,799 --> 00:14:20,240
Are you sure

159
00:14:21,200 --> 00:14:22,799
you've thought it through?

160
00:14:23,320 --> 00:14:23,919
Yes.

161
00:14:28,279 --> 00:14:30,519
Whatever you want, I can grant it.

162
00:14:31,720 --> 00:14:34,720
But I will not allow you to marry her.

163
00:14:40,519 --> 00:14:41,679
Where are you going?

164
00:14:43,879 --> 00:14:46,320
The matters here have come to an end.

165
00:14:46,480 --> 00:14:49,159
The Xuanji Pavilion's arrangements
in Jiangnan have changed.

166
00:14:49,720 --> 00:14:50,480
I'll go check.

167
00:14:50,919 --> 00:14:54,120
You didn't come with us to the palace.
Have you already guessed?

168
00:14:54,879 --> 00:14:56,200
That man's identity.

169
00:14:57,279 --> 00:15:02,200
Later, Lianyi had an accident.
I couldn't save her.

170
00:15:02,639 --> 00:15:07,080
I only managed to snatch back
the child taken by the assassins.

171
00:15:07,600 --> 00:15:11,200
That child was Gu Zhaoxi.

172
00:15:12,159 --> 00:15:14,000
Since we already know who Zhaoxi is,

173
00:15:14,320 --> 00:15:16,159
his identity isn't hard to guess.

174
00:15:18,720 --> 00:15:20,399
Nothing can be hidden from you.

175
00:15:21,480 --> 00:15:23,879
You two planned
that whole wedding scene together.

176
00:15:24,159 --> 00:15:25,440
You knew he wasn't dead.

177
00:15:25,919 --> 00:15:28,879
Or did you do that
because he hid who he really was

178
00:15:29,440 --> 00:15:30,120
and lied to you?

179
00:15:30,919 --> 00:15:34,200
It happened so fast.
I tried to play along,

180
00:15:34,720 --> 00:15:37,559
using a trick dagger to fake his death.

181
00:15:38,159 --> 00:15:40,000
But a retracting dagger wasn't enough.

182
00:15:40,559 --> 00:15:43,960
If the wound didn't bleed,
the secret would be out.

183
00:15:44,720 --> 00:15:47,799
So I thought of cutting my palm
to create a diversion.

184
00:15:49,759 --> 00:15:50,759
But he...

185
00:16:10,919 --> 00:16:14,519
I kept telling myself
that he understood my idea.

186
00:16:15,759 --> 00:16:17,240
But I wasn't injured.

187
00:16:26,960 --> 00:16:28,000
And I wasn't sure

188
00:16:28,759 --> 00:16:31,000
if he pressed the gem on the dagger.

189
00:16:31,919 --> 00:16:33,720
Perhaps that's worry
clouding your judgment.

190
00:16:34,480 --> 00:16:36,159
Now, everything is back on track.

191
00:16:36,759 --> 00:16:37,440
That's fine.

192
00:16:37,720 --> 00:16:40,600
Father, why must you
oppose this marriage?

193
00:16:40,759 --> 00:16:43,919
Back then, didn't you and Mother
go against everyone to be together?

194
00:16:43,919 --> 00:16:45,480
And you made her brother a general.

195
00:16:45,799 --> 00:16:48,120
But in the end, I couldn't protect her.

196
00:16:56,720 --> 00:16:59,240
If you truly want to stand
against all opposition and marry her,

197
00:16:59,879 --> 00:17:02,399
you must consider if you can
protect her for a lifetime.

198
00:17:07,160 --> 00:17:09,400
But haven't you two performed
the wedding ceremony?

199
00:17:10,640 --> 00:17:13,920
Chaosheng, mind your words.
That was just a stopgap.

200
00:17:14,160 --> 00:17:16,480
After all, he is
the Crown Prince, and I...

201
00:17:17,279 --> 00:17:19,000
Now, I'm the Marquis of Yong'an.

202
00:17:19,839 --> 00:17:21,400
If you want to enter the palace,

203
00:17:21,640 --> 00:17:23,440
I will stand as your unwavering support.

204
00:17:23,920 --> 00:17:26,160
Aren't you the one
who hates getting involved in trouble?

205
00:17:26,960 --> 00:17:30,680
You even talked of selling everything.
Why did you accept the ennobling?

206
00:17:33,240 --> 00:17:34,400
If you choose Jiangnan,

207
00:17:34,799 --> 00:17:35,960
I'll sell off

208
00:17:35,960 --> 00:17:37,519
all the shops here and go with you.

209
00:17:39,240 --> 00:17:44,839
But if you choose to enter the palace,
I will be your support forever.

210
00:17:46,599 --> 00:17:48,119
So our days of affection

211
00:17:48,359 --> 00:17:51,200
were a "stopgap" to you?

212
00:17:53,920 --> 00:17:54,480
Chaosheng.

213
00:18:06,759 --> 00:18:10,000
Though unremarkable,
I've still offered my support to you.

214
00:18:10,599 --> 00:18:12,000
You previously promised

215
00:18:12,200 --> 00:18:16,000
that I could freely share
any questions or desires with you.

216
00:18:17,279 --> 00:18:17,839
Yes.

217
00:18:19,920 --> 00:18:22,119
There are thorny matters
within my household.

218
00:18:22,480 --> 00:18:25,000
Might you lend your assistance?

219
00:18:26,119 --> 00:18:26,920
What is it?

220
00:18:28,960 --> 00:18:30,240
I have a beloved,

221
00:18:31,079 --> 00:18:34,359
but she lied and told me she was
in love with my elder brother.

222
00:18:34,960 --> 00:18:38,079
That troubles me deeply,
even robbing me of sleep.

223
00:18:40,680 --> 00:18:42,160
Did Chaosheng tell you?

224
00:18:45,079 --> 00:18:47,759
That day, you came just in time.

225
00:18:48,279 --> 00:18:49,160
But Gu Jiang...

226
00:18:50,519 --> 00:18:53,880
The family head felt
he didn't deserve to return to his sect.

227
00:18:54,240 --> 00:18:57,640
Chaosheng and I agreed
to send his remains to the Tianji Sect.

228
00:18:59,160 --> 00:19:01,400
As for why I infiltrated
the palace that day,

229
00:19:01,720 --> 00:19:04,240
didn't you say to act in seven days?

230
00:19:05,960 --> 00:19:07,960
When will the frost and snow return?

231
00:19:09,680 --> 00:19:10,920
May we meet again

232
00:19:12,400 --> 00:19:13,599
when spirits return.

233
00:19:18,079 --> 00:19:22,200
I told you if I left again,
I'd tell you my return date.

234
00:19:25,480 --> 00:19:27,799
If I journey far again,
I'll tell you my return date.

235
00:19:29,440 --> 00:19:30,240
- Great.
- Great.

236
00:19:30,519 --> 00:19:32,000
So beautiful.

237
00:19:47,319 --> 00:19:50,440
I'm truly blessed to have found
someone as clever as you in this life.

238
00:19:53,519 --> 00:19:56,319
Failing to spend it with you
would leave me with lifelong regret.

239
00:19:59,279 --> 00:20:02,640
We still have an unfinished game
in the Fufeng Pavilion.

240
00:20:03,200 --> 00:20:05,640
And I haven't fully mastered
the techniques you taught me.

241
00:20:06,960 --> 00:20:09,824
Since your family affairs
concluded with the wedding,

242
00:20:10,592 --> 00:20:13,759
let mine begin with it.

243
00:20:15,759 --> 00:20:17,400
My family is a bit complicated.

244
00:20:17,720 --> 00:20:20,920
After the wedding,
I'll tell you all of it.

245
00:20:21,440 --> 00:20:22,599
What do you think?

246
00:20:23,880 --> 00:20:25,839
I want to protect her all her life.

247
00:20:26,359 --> 00:20:28,359
But she's not someone I need to protect,

248
00:20:28,640 --> 00:20:31,200
but someone strong enough
to stand side by side with me.

249
00:20:34,200 --> 00:20:36,880
So, will you lend a hand?

250
00:20:40,314 --> 00:20:44,608
♪Because my heart
knew you at first sight♪

251
00:20:46,215 --> 00:20:51,666
♪I want to hold tight
this love on the wind♪

252
00:20:53,434 --> 00:20:58,689
♪Our stolen moment passes too soon♪

253
00:20:59,225 --> 00:21:05,838
♪Unable to wait for this love to bloom♪

254
00:21:07,529 --> 00:21:09,769
♪Who isn't just a passerby♪

255
00:21:09,769 --> 00:21:12,489
♪And whose only one are you♪

256
00:21:12,771 --> 00:21:14,121
♪Who broke♪

257
00:21:14,435 --> 00:21:15,865
♪Whose heart♪

258
00:21:16,035 --> 00:21:18,461
♪Yet find it hard to part♪

259
00:21:19,427 --> 00:21:22,640
♪Trapped in pain's shallows♪

260
00:21:22,825 --> 00:21:25,609
♪Letting tears run wild♪

